snippet.title: Galaxy Highways - Demo Announcement
snippet.description:
We are very excited to make an announcement that Galaxy Highways will release free demo on February 2nd 2023!

The demo will have proper tutorial, 3 standard levels and one special level, where you'll be able to play with the battleship! You can choose from 3 different ships and you will be able to unlock and upgrade a lot of different secondary and special weapons.

Wishlist our game if you haven't done that already and don't forget that you can also join our Discord 👉 https://discord.gg/vJ8QdVv for some more news, discussions or to join our testing squad.
